data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Ventana subdivision in Bulverde, TX! This stunning two-story residence, built in 2022, offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless design. With 5 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, and a wealth of sophisticated features, this home is an embodiment of comfort and style. As you enter, the grand foyer welcomes you with its soaring ceilings and an abundance of natural light. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the spacious living area, elegant dining space, and gourmet kitchen, creating an ideal space for both entertaining and everyday living. The chef-inspired kitchen boasts top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, bright countertops, and a large center island - a culinary haven for any aspiring chef. The main floor master suite is a true retreat, offering a serene escape with its spa-like ensuite bath featuring dual vanities, a luxurious soaking tub, and a separate walk-in shower. Downstairs you will also find a study, powder room, media room, and a secondary guest suite with a private full bath. Upstairs, you'll find three more generously sized bedrooms, each with ample closet space and easy access to well-appointed bathrooms. This home also features a versatile loft area that can be used as a playroom or additional living space. The backyard is an oasis for relaxation and perfectly situated with a covered patio for outdoor dining and a spacious yard for gatherings. This property backs up to a greenbelt, so there's plenty of privacy if you would like to add a pool. Situated in the sought-after Ventana subdivision, and its prime location in Bulverde, you'll have convenient access to the award winning Comal ISD schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of luxury living in Bulverde's Ventana subdivision! Owner has a assumable loan at 5.25% upon qualification.
